      <title>比特币价格剧烈波动表明 ETF 买家的影响力不断上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/bitcoin-s-wild-price-swings-point-to-the-rising-influence-of-etf-buyers</link>
